s shares in dish said that the company is very uncooperative he says that despite traveling to denver frequently has never been able to get a meeting with ergen or any other dish senior manager “they’re probably the least transparent company of any i’ve ever dealt with personal lifeedit ergen was born into an episcopalian family in oak ridge tennessee on march   the fourth of five children born to viola née siebenthal and william krasny ergen his mother was one of the first female accountants in the state of minnesota his father was an austrian immigrant who was working in sweden as a nuclear physicist and left europe prior to world war ii his father coined the phrase china syndrome his parents married in minnesota in  and then moved to camden new jersey before settling in oak ridge where his father accepted a position at the oak ridge national laboratory ergen received a bachelor of arts from the university of tennessee at knoxville and an mba from wake forest university he was a professional blackjack and poker player he is married to cantey candy mcadam they have five children they live in littleton colorado ergen is an avid mountain climber who has scaled mount kilimanjaro mount aconcagua in argentina and mount everest base camp in nepal he is a member of the colorado mountain club and has climbed all of colorado’s foot peaks besides mountain climbing his interests include poker and pickup basketball awardsedit in june  ergen was named ‘master entrepreneur of the year’ for the rocky mountain region by inc magazine two years prior he had been honoured with a home satellite tv association star award ergen played a key role in fighting for american consumers’ rights to watch local television channels via satellite which became a reality after the satellite home viewer improvement act was passed in  he has been an advocate of video competition issues and testified before the congress in this regard on numerous occasions he was recognized with a rocky mountain news’ business person of the year award in  and honoured a second time in  ergen also won the frost  sullivan  ceo of the year of the satellite industry in  he was named ‘space industry business man of the year’ ergen was named one of the ‘world’s best ceos’ by barron’s magazine in  he was also mentioned in forbes magazine ‘top ten ceos’ list ergen cofounded the satellite broadcasting and communications association referencesedit  a b c d e charles ergen forbes   httpswwwsecgovarchivesedgardataadefahtm  dish managementteam dish   a b charles ergen wall street journal wsj   a b echostar accounting raises flags in probe people say bloomberg  march    a b dish network corpa businessweek   a b c d e businessweek resume businessweek    wealthiest people in colorado imfromcoloradocom  retrieved    a b chairman and chief executive officer echostar communications corporation   a b echostar to acquire hughes for about  billion bloomberg  february    dish networks intriguing  acquisitions  december    echostar announces completion of merger with dbsc thefreelibrarycom   echostar communications corporation history fundinguniversecom   sling media to be acquired by echostar for  million gizmodo  september    dish network to buy satellite firm for  billion wsjcom  february    dish network acquires blockbuster for  million in cash huffingtonpostcom  april    dish’s  billion terrestar purchase approved by us bankruptcy judge bloomberg  july    dish network ceo charlie ergen the tv disrupter advertising age  december    federal court wont block dishs ‘autohop’ multichannel   dishs autohop scores another legal win los angeles times   a b c d e f g dish network the meanest company in america bloombergcom  retrieved    jonathan stempel harbinger sues dish ergen over lightsquared seeks  billion reuters july   kurt orzeck dish ergen escape harbingers b suit over lightsquared law april    httpwwwhollywoodreportercomthresqshareholderssuedishcharlieergen  female echostar executives charge ergen 