rts home dish newsroom home charlie ergen charlie ergen charlie ergen cofounder chairman of the board and chief executive officer download photos charlieergenjpg  kb emailpdfprintrss charlie ergen cofounded dish formerly echostar communications corporation more than  years ago and currently acts as chairman of the board of directors for both dish and echostar as ceo he oversees dishs longterm business development from  to  in his role as chairman charlie focused on reaching new markets and expanding product and service offerings including sling tv and the acquisition of additional wireless spectrum a prominent leader in the satellite and telecommunications industries charlie has received numerous accolades for his career as an entrepreneur he was among the  class of inductees into the consumer electronics hall of fame and was named one of barron’s “world’s best ceos” and listed among forbes top  ceos” in  in  charlie was honored as frost  sullivan’s “ceo of the year in the satellite industry” award and became the first person to win the rocky mountain news business person of the year” for the second time instrumental in the fight to allow american consumers access to local channels via satellite he helped secure the passage of the satellite home viewer improvement act in  and was cofounder of the satellite broadcasting communications association  charlie received his bachelor of science in general business and accounting from the university of tennessee and his master of business administration from the babcock graduate school of management at wake forest university an avid mountain climber and member of the colorado mountain club charlie has climbed all of the state’s  thousand foot peaks scaled mount kilimanjaro in tanzania mount aconcagua in argentina and the mount everest base camp in nepal he enjoys spending time with candy his wife of more than  years and their five children download photos charlieergenjpg  kb navigate dish newsroom about dish dish news dish cares images  videos contact us email alerts visit other dish sites investor relations dish careers dish cares dishcom dishlatino dish for business dish international dish media sales dish highspeed internet smart phone repair sling tv dish dishnews   dish network llc all rights reserved privacy policy sitemap business wire newshqsm